metadata.name: Pumpa IRL Genesis Edition 1/5
metadata.description: Pumpametti's IRL artwork titles as NFT trading cards. Every physical Pumpametti artwork will come with one of these bad boys. Plz make sure to transfer the Metti physical art along with the title NFT trading card. Plz do not buy/trade Metti physical art if it does not have the title NFT trading card. PUMPA IRL GENESIS EDITION, 2022, SERIALE 1/5, ARCHIVAL LAMBDA PRINT ON PAPER, 24x24 INCHES. The genesis owner of this title NFT trading card will receive the corresponding physical artwork, with shipping costs covered by the artist. LFG! https://www.pumpametti.com/
